{"tid":1468040,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（求下你睇) 其實我地贏緊","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T20:14:42.000Z","uid":6408,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d695abea38091aa0c78f34a8b7721809405f95a3","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母諗下我地呢深個月嚟係點走到今日！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割席 不篤灰<br />\n前線行動由前線決定<br />\n記得嗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚前線捉咗個大陸佬嚟打<br />\n係中計又點？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">您諗下811<br />\n比班曱甴射盲嘅隊友<br />\n比班曱甴打崩牙嘅隊友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ew42yxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Few42yxW.jpg&h=e3aae5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTJuXZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTJuXZC.jpg&h=e5648f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再諗下721<br />\n比班癲佬打嘅無辜市民...</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abVtt5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabVtt5Z.jpg&h=e89c247e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比之下今晚前線做嘅嘢<br />\n算得係啲乜?<br />\n你問你自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢排呢度係好撚多鬼吹風<br />\n但係<br />\n我哋香港原有嘅係上面無嘅獨立思考能力<br />\n天琦講過嫁嘛<br />\n&ldquo;要時刻保持頭腦清醒&rdquo;<br />\n記得嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係打大陸佬嘅片會失民心<br />\n咁又點？<br />\n我哋從來都唔需要佢哋嘅民心<br />\n呢個係香港人嘅運動呀</span><br />\n更何況我哋今晚有嘅係係<span style=\"color: red;\">全球記者</span>嘅紀錄下<br />\n令對家大腦出醜<br />\n佢哋話無過唔會干預架嘛<br />\n用呢點合理化嚟做文宣啦!!!<br />\n<br />\n係今日嘅香港<br />\n我地無可咁理性嫁啦<br />\n<em><strong>冷靜落嚟 討論下下一步點做好無？</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勿忙初心 <br />\n我地一個都不能少<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndLEAMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndLEAMK.jpg&h=6496c710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfadaae813046f1752cd4de41e0e524ee150ef59","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:59.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c14db725440720eb6c54e43074d540060b54d2eb","tid":1468040,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"3ee42aa1020af5ad8f001c3335e6d1658f29d2ee","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d48415b298b8719d5e24ba400a9b8d11a49717d6","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"236c6b82cb4dceb913e53465cfc8aa5dac074104","tid":1468040,"uid":125150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"示威手足做錯，<br />\n<br />\n請不要指責，不要心灰意冷，<br />\n<br />\n而是去討論，去幫手足「補獲」。<br />\n<br />\n「不分化，不割席」是個莊嚴的誓言，<br />\n<br />\n講到必須做到。"},{"pid":"670cbfe1e31c3f38f6afe1ce43c3c7301ff888a0","tid":1468040,"uid":288475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">推啊</span>"},{"pid":"92a5d4aa737e9ab3df26bc45aff170e483a8638d","tid":1468040,"uid":131259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"講真 運動行到今時今日唔單單下兄弟爬山<br />\n無民意神早收左皮"},{"pid":"001b1294478671dc9fb60350689ce3942d657ce0","tid":1468040,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"又要話黑狗係恐襲組織，打人、主動阻旅客咪一樣比人話返轉頭。民意點會無用呢<br />\n<br />\n不過發生左就算，以後：<br />\n<br />\n和理非回合，勇武尊重<br />\n<br />\n勇武回會，和理非配合<br />\n<br />\n互補長短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場呢鋪係和理非場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要人，就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"e1c1f367a87c854e8ad9b91fd419da1b2e2482f0","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92a5d4aa737e9ab3df26bc45aff170e483a8638d","tid":1468040,"uid":131259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"講真 運動行到今時今日唔單單下兄弟爬山<br />\n無民意神早收左皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:00.000Z","msg":"係 我明<br />\n但你諗番71<br />\n只要我哋唔割一定得<br />\n對家都唔係神<br />\n佢地好撚蠢㗎"},{"pid":"ac0e0c1157f85a7100080114f0364323a831019a","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001b1294478671dc9fb60350689ce3942d657ce0","tid":1468040,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"又要話黑狗係恐襲組織，打人、主動阻旅客咪一樣比人話返轉頭。民意點會無用呢<br />\n<br />\n不過發生左就算，以後：<br />\n<br />\n和理非回合，勇武尊重<br />\n<br />\n勇武回會，和理非配合<br />\n<br />\n互補長短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場呢鋪係和理非場合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要人，就係咁簡單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:36.000Z","msg":"我哋係同一team ga"},{"pid":"11e0c26258aca9fed70766213d10f12b82d93e4f","tid":1468040,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d695abea38091aa0c78f34a8b7721809405f95a3","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母諗下我地呢深個月嚟係點走到今日！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割席 不篤灰<br />\n前線行動由前線決定<br />\n記得嗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚前線捉咗個大陸佬嚟打<br />\n係中計又點？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">您諗下811<br />\n比班曱甴射盲嘅隊友<br />\n比班曱甴打崩牙嘅隊友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ew42yxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Few42yxW.jpg&h=e3aae5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTJuXZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTJuXZC.jpg&h=e5648f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再諗下721<br />\n比班癲佬打嘅無辜市民...</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abVtt5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabVtt5Z.jpg&h=e89c247e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比之下今晚前線做嘅嘢<br />\n算得係啲乜?<br />\n你問你自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢排呢度係好撚多鬼吹風<br />\n但係<br />\n我哋香港原有嘅係上面無嘅獨立思考能力<br />\n天琦講過嫁嘛<br />\n&ldquo;要時刻保持頭腦清醒&rdquo;<br />\n記得嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係打大陸佬嘅片會失民心<br />\n咁又點？<br />\n我哋從來都唔需要佢哋嘅民心<br />\n呢個係香港人嘅運動呀</span><br />\n更何況我哋今晚有嘅係係<span style=\"color: red;\">全球記者</span>嘅紀錄下<br />\n令對家大腦出醜<br />\n佢哋話無過唔會干預架嘛<br />\n用呢點合理化嚟做文宣啦!!!<br />\n<br />\n係今日嘅香港<br />\n我地無可咁理性嫁啦<br />\n<em><strong>冷靜落嚟 討論下下一步點做好無？</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勿忙初心 <br />\n我地一個都不能少<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndLEAMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndLEAMK.jpg&h=6496c710&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"冇民心<br />\n每次出黎比街坊吊到七彩既係你而唔係警察<br />\n而且我完全睇唔出點樣「令對家大腦出醜」<br />\n一兩個輔助公安就叫出醜<br />\n成班ON9拎張護照當係委任證<br />\n實證唔足夠..只有網上既身份對照<br />\n對家唔承認真係引唔起國際回響<br />\n<br />\n手兄處理手段又唔夠好<br />\n現場係比人帶晒風向<br />\n場面係真心令人反感<br />\n依家其實應該要有現場人士<br />\n搜集下兩個公安煽動現場情況既證據<br />\n先可以將依件事拉上去高層面"},{"pid":"2f5a22683061ece122172b2b2096443157434763","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e0c26258aca9fed70766213d10f12b82d93e4f","tid":1468040,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d695abea38091aa0c78f34a8b7721809405f95a3","tid":1468040,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母諗下我地呢深個月嚟係點走到今日！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割席 不篤灰<br />\n前線行動由前線決定<br />\n記得嗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚前線捉咗個大陸佬嚟打<br />\n係中計又點？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">您諗下811<br />\n比班曱甴射盲嘅隊友<br />\n比班曱甴打崩牙嘅隊友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ew42yxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Few42yxW.jpg&h=e3aae5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTJuXZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTJuXZC.jpg&h=e5648f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再諗下721<br />\n比班癲佬打嘅無辜市民...</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abVtt5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabVtt5Z.jpg&h=e89c247e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比之下今晚前線做嘅嘢<br />\n算得係啲乜?<br />\n你問你自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢排呢度係好撚多鬼吹風<br />\n但係<br />\n我哋香港原有嘅係上面無嘅獨立思考能力<br />\n天琦講過嫁嘛<br />\n&ldquo;要時刻保持頭腦清醒&rdquo;<br />\n記得嗎？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係打大陸佬嘅片會失民心<br />\n咁又點？<br />\n我哋從來都唔需要佢哋嘅民心<br />\n呢個係香港人嘅運動呀</span><br />\n更何況我哋今晚有嘅係係<span style=\"color: red;\">全球記者</span>嘅紀錄下<br />\n令對家大腦出醜<br />\n佢哋話無過唔會干預架嘛<br />\n用呢點合理化嚟做文宣啦!!!<br />\n<br />\n係今日嘅香港<br />\n我地無可咁理性嫁啦<br />\n<em><strong>冷靜落嚟 討論下下一步點做好無？</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勿忙初心 <br />\n我地一個都不能少<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndLEAMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndLEAMK.jpg&h=6496c710&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"冇民心<br />\n每次出黎比街坊吊到七彩既係你而唔係警察<br />\n而且我完全睇唔出點樣「令對家大腦出醜」<br />\n一兩個輔助公安就叫出醜<br />\n成班ON9拎張護照當係委任證<br />\n實證唔足夠..只有網上既身份對照<br />\n對家唔承認真係引唔起國際回響<br />\n<br />\n手兄處理手段又唔夠好<br />\n現場係比人帶晒風向<br />\n場面係真心令人反感<br />\n依家其實應該要有現場人士<br />\n搜集下兩個公安煽動現場情況既證據<br />\n先可以將依件事拉上去高層面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"作咪得囉 我地都可以整fake news ga"},{"pid":"67de2e677f90ddc0752680630b3fb37863361eba","tid":1468040,"uid":31773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"但郁fa記者一定有錯<br />\n阻礙人道救援一定有問題"},{"pid":"00314b